abstract: David Lingmerth shoots seven-under-par 65 for one-shot lead at Memorial Tournament and Tiger Woods barely makes cut; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: David Lingmerth had a seven-under-par 65 at the Memorial Tournament in Dublin, Ohio, and a one-shot lead. Tiger Woods made the cut on the number.

headline.print_headline: Sports Briefing | Golf; Woods Barely Makes Cut
